{
  "stem": "15694.6",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they let us go because for them, they couldn't-- I'm sure they couldn't care less whether there's one more, you know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it would have taken away from the drinking time of the evening, I suppose, if they had to, to report somebody missing.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Probably they shrugged their shoulders and that was it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I just hoped that was another successful escape.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I was going to do that, but then I get a shock when somebody else did it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now I came to the place where there were, I would say-- that's guesswork-- but 2,00 people lining up and marching in fives, as they usually do, in rows of fives, away from that place.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, what's going on?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I thought-- I asked them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, they took a number of people there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, did they take anybody from the metal workshops?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No, no, nobody from the metal workshops.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I thought, well, that's important.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Money [INAUDIBLE] for whatever you produce probably goes into the commandant's pockets.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] anyway, I was told my father wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The next thing was I had to get out of that group.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But how will I get out of that group?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So-- well, again, I was thinking if the commandant needs people to shoot, he's not shy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He would shoot anyway.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And what will he do with people at night?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I couldn't make head or tail what it is.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I said whatever it is, I mustn't go to the-- you know, to line up wherever those, those people went.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And anyway, I lined up and marched forward, looking for an opportunity to get away.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
